Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:44.82,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}惡い夢でもているようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:44.82,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1}{\an9}warui yume demo miteru youda
